\;n=1\;
49^{n+1}-2352(n+1)-1=49\cdot 49^n-2352n-2352-1=
=49(49^n-2352n-1)+(48n-1)2352+48
(48n-1)2352+48=48\left[1+49(48n-1)\right]=\underbrace{48}_{=2^4\cdot3}\left[3\cdot 2^4\cdot 7^3n-3\cdot 2^4\right]=
=2^83^2\left[7^3n-1\right] 
\;2304=2^83^2\;
48^2=2304,
49^n=(1+48)^n=1+48n+48^2(\cdots)\equiv1+48n\pmod{48^2}
48\equiv48+2304\pmod{2304}\equiv2352\implies48n\equiv2352n\pmod{2304}
